---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = '/tradfi-onchain';
---

<Layout title="Bridging Traditional Finance and Onchain Markets">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-16">
    <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">For Hong Kong Finance Professionals</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
      Bridging Traditional Finance<br/>and <span class="text-cyan-400">Onchain Markets</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-3xl mb-12">
      A practical guide to prediction markets, perpetual exchanges, and automated market making — for investment bankers, fund managers, family offices, and trading desks in Hong Kong.
    </p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">$2.9B</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">BlackRock BUIDL<br/>Tokenized Treasuries AUM</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">$1.5T+</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">JP Morgan Kinexys<br/>Total Transactions Processed</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">HK$10B</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">Hong Kong Government<br/>Tokenized Green Bond</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">$600M</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">ICE (NYSE Parent)<br/>Investment in Polymarket</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Who Is This For</h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-500 mb-8">Whether you're exploring these markets personally or evaluating them for your business, this guide provides the context you need.</p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium text-sm mb-2">Investment Banking</p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">ECM/DCM teams exploring tokenized issuance. Structured products moving onchain. New advisory opportunities in digital assets.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium text-sm mb-2">Asset Management</p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">Funds seeking onchain yield, new asset classes, and 24/7 market access. Tokenized treasuries as collateral.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium text-sm mb-2">Family Offices</p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">52% of HK family offices plan crypto allocation. Digital assets now qualify for tax concessions under the new regime.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium text-sm mb-2">Prop Trading</p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">24/7 perpetual futures, pre-IPO exposure via HIP-3, onchain arbitrage opportunities, and funding rate strategies.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium text-sm mb-2">Compliance & Risk</p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">Understanding DeFi products within the SFC regulatory framework. Preparing for upcoming VA dealer and custodian licensing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Three Onchain Products to Understand</h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-500 mb-8">Each represents a fundamental financial primitive — rebuilt on blockchain infrastructure.</p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <a href={`${base}/products/polymarket`} class="group bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-cyan-800/50 transition-colors">
        <p class="text-sm text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-2">Prediction Market</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">Polymarket</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm mb-4">Trade on the outcome of real-world events. Binary contracts priced by market consensus — from Fed rate decisions to AI model rankings. ICE (NYSE parent) invested $600M.</p>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 text-sm">30-day volume: $9.7B →</p>
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}/products/hyperliquid`} class="group bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-cyan-800/50 transition-colors">
        <p class="text-sm text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-2">Perpetual Exchange + Pre-IPO</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">Hyperliquid</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm mb-4">Crypto perpetual futures with up to 50x leverage. HIP-3 enables pre-IPO valuation exposure to SpaceX, OpenAI, Anthropic, and Cursor.</p>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 text-sm">Daily volume: $5-10B →</p>
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}/products/amm`} class="group bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-cyan-800/50 transition-colors">
        <p class="text-sm text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-2">Automated Market Making</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">Onchain AMM</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm mb-4">Permissionless markets where anyone can trade, provide liquidity, or launch new tokens. No exchange license or listing approval required.</p>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 text-sm">Uniswap daily volume: $1-2B →</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Why Now</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-3">Regulatory Clarity</p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">Hong Kong has licensed 12 virtual asset trading platforms, passed a stablecoin ordinance, and introduced tax concessions for family offices investing in digital assets. The framework is here.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-3">Institutional Adoption</p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">BlackRock, JP Morgan, Goldman Sachs, Citadel Securities, and the NYSE are all building onchain positions. This is no longer experimental — it's infrastructure investment by the world's largest financial institutions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-3">Infrastructure Maturity</p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">Sub-second settlement, $10B+ daily DEX volume, professional-grade APIs and tooling. The technology has reached the point where serious capital can operate reliably.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">🌍 Global Moves</h3>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">BlackRock</span> — BUIDL tokenized Treasuries fund, $2.9B AUM across 9 chains, accepted as collateral on Binance</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">JP Morgan</span> — Kinexys platform processing $1.5T+ in transactions, onchain FX settlement live</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Goldman Sachs</span> — GS DAP private blockchain, EIB €100M bond issuance, spinning out as industry utility mid-2026</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Citadel Securities</span> — $200M investment into Kraken at $20B valuation, expanding into crypto market-making</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">NYSE × Securitize</span> — MOU to build 24/7 tokenized securities trading platform</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">🇭🇰 Hong Kong</h3>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">HK Government</span> — Third tokenized green bond issuance, HK$10B, settled using digital-fiat currencies via HSBC Orion</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">HSBC</span> — Tokenized deposits live in HK, Singapore, UK. Orion institutional digital asset platform operational</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Standard Chartered</span> — First G-SIB to offer spot crypto trading. Banking partner for HashKey Exchange</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Family Offices</span> — 3,380+ in HK. 52% plan crypto allocation. Digital assets qualify for tax concessions</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">12 Licensed VATPs</span> — HashKey and OSL leading, retail access to BTC/ETH, institutional access broader</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-950/30 to-zinc-900/50 border border-green-900/30 rounded-xl p-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Questions? Let's Talk.</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-8">Whether you're exploring these products for the first time or evaluating them for your business, we're happy to discuss.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/85256171671" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 bg-green-500 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-green-400 transition-colors">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
        WhatsApp: +852 5617 1671
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
